16 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
17 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
18 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 295 of Title 17, unless there is
19 created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
20 As used in this act:
21 1. “Certificate of authority” means authorization for a
22 transmission developer by an order of the Corporation Commission
23 through filing of a case with an application, notice, and hearing.
24
